<li id="cite&#95;note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222" /><cite id="CITEREFBlackwell" class="citation web cs1">Blackwell, Christopher W. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.stoa.org/demos/article_democracy_overview@page=3&amp;greekEncoding=UnicodeC.html">"Athenian Democracy: a brief overview&#160;!!!!"</a>. <i>www.stoa.org</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">31 July</span> 2024</span>.</cite><span title="ctx&#95;ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft&#95;val&#95;fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.stoa.org&amp;rft.atitle=Athenian+Democracy%3A+a+brief+overview+%21%21%21%21&amp;rft.aulast=Blackwell&amp;rft.aufirst=Christopher+W.&amp;rft&#95;id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stoa.org%2Fdemos%2Farticle&#95;democracy&#95;overview%40page%3D3%26greekEncoding%3DUnicodeC.html&amp;rfr&#95;id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAthenian+democracy" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite&#95;note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222" /><cite id="CITEREFVlastos1953" class="citation journal cs1">Vlastos, Gregory (1953). <span class="id-lock-subscription" title="Paid subscription required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307/292054">"Isonomia"</a></span>. <i>American Journal of Philology</i>. <b>74</b> (4): <span class="nowrap">337–</span>366. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.2307%2F292054">10.2307/292054</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/292054">292054</a>.</cite><span title="ctx&#95;ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft&#95;val&#95;fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=American+Journal+of+Philology&amp;rft.atitle=Isonomia&amp;rft.volume=74&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=337-366&amp;rft.date=1953&amp;rft&#95;id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F292054&amp;rft&#95;id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F292054%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft.aulast=Vlastos&amp;rft.aufirst=Gregory&amp;rft&#95;id=https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.2307%2F292054&amp;rfr&#95;id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAthenian+democracy" class="Z3988"></span></span>
