<li id="cite&#95;note-:1-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-:1_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:1_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:1_39-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:1_39-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222" /><cite id="CITEREFPritchard2014" class="citation journal cs1">Pritchard, David (2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://espace.library.uq.edu.au/data/UQ_328968/PRITCHARD_GREECE_AND_ROME_61_2014.pdf?Expires=1620174963&amp;Key-Pair-Id=APKAJKNBJ4MJBJNC6NLQ&amp;Signature=AMoEDvCcbfGi7NDRDV80X0wjii5CPj7eCmePGKphMgDOVOpYcbzu48AG5~NZJV7ZgwcFBNmZzu2Foq7e5CLFuxnwFzmvSkVJ0QJDuMskPQVUx93dGWeuyPg7rXYS29JOhiUJCkufFW9u-30s1soAw3FkRlgdEy5SBJrNPYXh-qtsUgItvmIyt2X8zeG-2f4Qf7EQftc~OCQGB~5oruTXq1XYRHBNR-7LsVjg1uaWdZXjNyaPMZgsbaNi4rZblNoS53IqX4RqUQZdyhtjfE5x6DbpCnSwkUox9w6VRT~UZTCmtuKhAtygUw9qXQvEF6CS5i8aOrFUr3gwHVOz1TUCfw__">"The Position of Attic Women in Democratic Athens"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>Greece and Rome</i>. <b>61</b> (2): <span class="nowrap">174–</span>193. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1017%2FS0017383514000072">10.1017/S0017383514000072</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:74391789">74391789</a>.</cite><span title="ctx&#95;ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft&#95;val&#95;fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Greece+and+Rome&amp;rft.atitle=The+Position+of+Attic+Women+in+Democratic+Athens&amp;rft.volume=61&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=174-193&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft&#95;id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1017%2FS0017383514000072&amp;rft&